		<descriptionSet>
			<description lang="eng" script="Latn">
				<text>The main illustration in this advertisement for &quot;Afghan Snow&quot; shows a woman from behind who holds a mirror in her left hand and looking at herself. She wears a silk skirt and leans back on two white pillows. Her black hair is tightly tied up and adorned with a rose. She wears pearl necklaces and earrings, and a ring on her left middle finger. Apparently, the illustration uses a range of stereotypical motifs of female beauty and the importance of body care.</text>
				<author>
					<name vocab="local" type="corporate" refid="uuid-492ff6ac-d4b8-5d8a-b6c9-58287f9184cb">PPColl_editors</name>
					<role vocab="marcrelator" code="edt">Editor</role>
				</author>
			</description>
			<description lang="eng" script="Latn">
				<text>There is a second illustration showing a pot of the cream, with its lid open. The opened pot is surrounded by different flowers.</text>
				<author>
					<name vocab="local" type="corporate" refid="uuid-492ff6ac-d4b8-5d8a-b6c9-58287f9184cb">PPColl_editors</name>
					<role vocab="marcrelator" code="edt">Editor</role>
				</author>
			</description>
		</descriptionSet>
